    "description": "LOOTBAWX let's you collect unique loot by opening <i>free</i> loot boxes. <br><br>You will be awarded a free loot box between every 30 minutes and 2 hours as long as you are playing the game. It is your choice whether to open the crate, sell the crate, or even trade your loot on the marketplace to other fellow LOOTBAWXers!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REGULAR DROPS</h2>Loot crates dropped every hour and new ones released weekly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/22330747745a51fae9955436705c4ac8.poster.avif?t=1723603837\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/22330747745a51fae9955436705c4ac8.webm?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/22330747745a51fae9955436705c4ac8.mp4?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WEAR VALUE, ITEMS GUARANTEED UNIQUE</h2>Loot has WEAR VALUE meaning each item you receive is UNIQUE. NO OTHER CLICKERS HAVE THIS! Each item also has rarity and special effects can be rolled too!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/8ba3470b6b82da470786e401dc8ed984.avif?t=1723603837\" width=440 height=226 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACTABLES</h2>Interactable items such as guns which actually shoot!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/61bfc58d33f083aaed673e065bcef487.poster.avif?t=1723603837\" width=800 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/61bfc58d33f083aaed673e065bcef487.webm?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/61bfc58d33f083aaed673e065bcef487.mp4?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHOP, BUY AND SELL</h2>Shop where you can SELL your low tier loot for COINS and BUY crates.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/4dbbbbdb1a93e598eed801950c31f059.avif?t=1723603837\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras_big/4dbbbbdb1a93e598eed801950c31f059.avif?t=1723603837 width=800 height=416 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VIRTUAL PLINKO</h2>We even have PLINKO where you can roll to get coins buy even more crates!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/7ce0b0f8e67620d03d45a56e3eff571c.poster.avif?t=1723603837\" width=800 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/7ce0b0f8e67620d03d45a56e3eff571c.webm?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/7ce0b0f8e67620d03d45a56e3eff571c.mp4?t=1723603837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Party system!</h2>Join your friends to get loot faster!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3108710/extras/8202596976d4e1d8e12b5a6b9230c13b.avif?t=1723603837\" width=768 height=430 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >... And many more features</h2>- Tons of steam achievements<br>- Friendly discord ^_^<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upcoming features</h2>Beyond looting, we're also close to releasing a few features to make this an even better experience including both a FLEX and WAGER mode. In FLEX mode you get paired against a fellow player in a minigame and can flex your loot; WAGER mode is a winner-takes-all minigame where you can wager your loot and the winning player takes all the spoils.<br><br>Please join our discord and give feedback on what you would like to see!",
